### [Genesis Chapter 45](../../../bib/kjv/gen045.htm#001.md)

[Genesis](../../../bib/kjv/gen001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">gen 45:0</span></span>

Overview

[Gen 45:1](../../../bib/kjv/gen045.htm#001.md), Joseph makes himself known
to his brethren; [Gen 45:5](../../../bib/kjv/gen045.htm#005.md), He
comforts them in God's providence; [Gen
45:9](../../../bib/kjv/gen045.htm#009.md), He sends for his father; [Gen
45:16](../../../bib/kjv/gen045.htm#016.md), Pharaoh confirms it; [Gen
45:21](../../../bib/kjv/gen045.htm#021.md), Joseph furnishes then for their
journey, and exhorts them to concord; [Gen
45:25](../../../bib/kjv/gen045.htm#025.md), Jacob is revived with the news.

